cs.GT, cs.MA, cs.NI, cs.DS, cs.LG

The paper focuses on designing incentive mechanisms for mobile crowdsourced sensing, which involves game theory and multi-agent systems (cs.GT, cs.MA). It also involves networked systems and online algorithms (cs.NI), as well as data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) for efficient computation. Finally, the paper evaluates the performance of the proposed mechanisms through simulations, which involves machine learning and statistical methods (cs.LG).
